01:11:11,093 --> 01:11:12,615
”What do you think of this Guru?” Don’t
bring me to controversies.

691
01:11:12,640 --> 01:11:13,595
It’s unnecessary.

692
01:11:13,620 --> 01:11:17,664
If they were of any value, you would have
been a realized soul.

693
01:11:17,689 --> 01:11:23,587
I can make out from you who was your Guru
