702
01:12:01,091 --> 01:12:04,457
If they wanted money, they could have smuggled.

703
01:12:04,482 --> 01:12:11,629
They could have done something like that,
but they should not have ruined your Kundalini.

704
01:12:11,654 --> 01:12:13,487
They had no business to do it.

705
01:12:13,487 --> 01:12:21,077
They will go to hell, no doubt, but they’ll
be carrying so many with them, they know that.

706
01:12:21,077 --> 01:12:23,377
They are trying to overpower.

707
01:12:23,377 --> 01:12:25,097
They are Anti-Christ.

708
01:12:25,097 --> 01:12:27,026
They think they can win over God.

709
01:12:27,051 --> 01:12:35,738
Let them know that God’s Powers are so powerful
that they can all be destroyed like this in

710
01:12:35,763 --> 01:12:36,543
