737
01:14:11,902 --> 01:14:17,992
Seeker: What is the best approach we can take
to go to Laxmi?

738
01:14:18,017 --> 01:14:22,977
Shri Mataji: I will tell you tomorrow about
Laxmi, where she is settled down.

739
01:14:22,977 --> 01:14:26,107
That’s what we are going to do, all the
Goddess, not one.

740
01:14:26,107 --> 01:14:28,147
All in one bundle.

741
01:14:28,147 --> 01:14:29,828
Now what do you say to that?

742
01:14:29,853 --> 01:14:32,899
Alright, good idea.

743
