774
01:16:18,153 --> 01:16:19,443
It’s my job.

775
01:16:19,841 --> 01:16:36,047
First of all you love yourself, have self-esteem,
know that you are the temple of God, Then

776
01:16:36,047 --> 01:16:40,447
