847
01:21:40,707 --> 01:21:42,257
There is the door, not here.

848
01:21:42,257 --> 01:21:43,277
That’s all.

849
01:21:43,277 --> 01:21:52,567
But rest of the people just keep your attention
absolutely loose.

850
01:21:52,567 --> 01:21:55,731
Now, close your eyes.

851
01:21:55,756 --> 01:22:03,852
Keep your eyes closed, because Kundalini has
to pass through Agnya chakra and if your eyes

852
01:22:03,927 --> 01:22:07,533
are not closed, she won’t rise.

853
01:22:07,558 --> 01:22:11,577
Put your hands towards me just like this.

854
01:22:11,577 --> 01:22:17,057
All of you, please put your hands, because
in the hands you have those centers.

855
01:22:17,057 --> 01:22:20,327
I would request you to take out if there is
anything heavy in your necks.

856
01:22:20,327 --> 01:22:21,567
Please, take off.

857
01:22:21,567 --> 01:22:22,807
It is better.

858
01:22:22,807 --> 01:22:27,147
Also, if there is anything heavy or tight
on your waist.

859
01:22:27,147 --> 01:22:37,617
You can loosen your belt a little bit.

860
01:22:37,617 --> 01:22:56,167
Just put your hands towards me.

861
01:22:56,167 --> 01:23:05,447
Close your eyes.

862
01:23:16,730 --> 01:23:30,727
Please, put your right hand on your heart,
because Spirit resides in our heart.

863
01:23:30,827 --> 01:23:35,407
Sit very comfortably without any strain on
your back.

864
01:23:35,407 --> 01:23:36,887
